#

Brussels Sprouts with Bacon and Maple Syrup

30 min
$10
220 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian OptionGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

Side DishQuickEasySavorySweet

Description

A deliciously sweet and savory side dish featuring crispy bacon and caramelized Brussels sprouts drizzled with maple syrup.

Ingredients

  • brussels sprouts: 1 lb
  • bacon: 4 slices
  • maple syrup: 2 tbsp
  • olive oil: 1 tbsp
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
